            int pos,
            java.lang.String start,

        Parameters:
        media - original uncut media link
        pos - the position of the clip in the timeline
        start - start time (relative to the media) of cut media hh:mm:ss.xxx if "" -> no cut in front
        end - length of the cut media in the timeline hh:mm:ss.xxx if "" -> whole cut media will be placed at pos
